        <body>
            <div>
                
            <pb facs="liv_000943_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> 
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><date when="1857-01-09">9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> <choice><abbr>Jany</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice> 1857</date></p>
<lb/>    
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>Zouga</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I have very
<lb/>little time to write
<lb/>you but as I
<lb/>wrote to <persName>Robert</persName>
<lb/><persName>Agnes</persName> &amp; <persName>Thomas</persName>
<lb/>I must send a
<lb/>line to you also</p>

 
<!-- No images of the following 2 pages are currently available as they are obscured by frame - they are therefore transcribed by copying an existing transcript (in same frame as pages 1 & 4 of the letter). This is not ideal as line breaks and other textual formatting features cannot be determined, nor can it be determined where the page break between 2 & 3 occurs. I have used <supplied> to mark these sections - AM-->	
	<!--<pb facs="liv_000943_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p><supplied>I hope you are a good boy and remembering your creator and his son <persName>Jesus</persName> with love every day of your life. He is so good to us all and it is good to feel that he is our father and friend and saviour all the way through life, watching over us and taking care of us by day and by night, in health and in sickness, in every place we go to and even in death, that you</supplied></p><space/>-->

	<!--<pb facs="liv_000943_0003" n="0003"/>-->

	<pb facs="liv_000943_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">must not fail
<lb/>to seek his favour
<lb/>and friendship
<lb/>His love is an
<lb/>inexpressible love
<lb/>He died for us
<lb/>through love. We
<lb/>cannot enjoy this
<lb/>love if we love
<lb/>sin.</p> <closer><salute>Kind kisses
<lb/>to all of you from
<lb/><persName>Mama</persName> &amp; me</salute>
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>
 
            </div>
